    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="P96-97">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Could I but ride indefinite,</l>
                    <l>As doth the meadow-bee,</l>
                    <l>And visit only where I liked,</l>
                    <l>And no man visit me,</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And flirt all day with buttercups,</l>
                    <l>And marry whom I may,</l>
                    <l>And dwell a little everywhere,</l>
                    <l>Or better, run away</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>With no police to follow,</l>
                    <l>Or chase me if I do,</l>
                    <l>Till I should jump peninsulas</l>
                    <l>To get away from you, </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I said, but just to be a bee</l>
                    <l>Upon a raft of air,</l>
                    <l>And row in nowhere all day long,</l>
                    <l>And anchor off the bar,</l>
                    <l>What liberty! So captives deem</l>
                    <l>Who tight in dungeons are.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
        </body>
